pgs are back, it is wonderful to have something to play that focuses on characters, writing and the game world, instead of just action, shooting or top of the line graphics like so many modern games these days.WRITING = 9.5/10WORLD DESIGN = 9/10SOUNDTRACK = 8.5/10COMBAT = 7/10NON-COMBAT GAMEPLAY = 9/10"
